WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:03.470
Hey, good morning family. How have y'all been

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:06.470
doing? I've been doing good. I just

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:09.430
had this on my heart.

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:11.230
I see so many people in the

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:13.910
comments below saying, 'Please pray for

00:00:13.910 --> 00:00:13.920
me.'I

00:00:13.920 --> 00:00:16.029
get a lot of emails from people asking for

00:00:16.039 --> 00:00:18.710
prayer for healing and deliverance,

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:21.509
needing new body parts, new

00:00:21.519 --> 00:00:23.670
organs, and all kinds of stuff.

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:26.150
There's nothing too big for our

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:29.150
God. I want to encourage you today that

00:00:29.160 --> 00:00:31.390
whatever it may be—you may be on

00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:34.750
death's doorstep, just seconds away from

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:36.470
stepping over into

00:00:36.470 --> 00:00:36.480
Glory—I

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:39.510
believe with all my

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:41.750
heart that it's never too late for a

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:44.709
divine miracle. It's never too late for

00:00:44.719 --> 00:00:47.189
God to heal you wherever you are. If

00:00:47.199 --> 00:00:48.430
you're in the hospital and you're

00:00:48.440 --> 00:00:50.590
watching this right now on your phone or

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:52.510
your laptop, or wherever you are at

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:55.110
the hospital, or you may be in hospice,

00:00:55.110 --> 00:00:55.120
or

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:56.990
at home and they've

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.349
released you and told you you're

00:00:58.359 --> 00:01:01.150
going to die in so many

00:01:01.150 --> 00:01:01.160
days—I'm

00:01:01.160 --> 00:01:04.109
telling you, nothing is impossible for

00:01:04.119 --> 00:01:07.749
our Lord. All things are possible

00:01:07.759 --> 00:01:10.910
to him that believes. I believe that

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:13.429
he became sick so that we don't have to

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:16.550
have sickness anymore. Galatians

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:19.230
says that Christ redeemed us from the

00:01:19.240 --> 00:01:21.390
curse of the law, and the curse of the

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:24.270
law is everything in Deuteronomy 28. If

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:26.109
you read all

00:01:26.119 --> 00:01:28.190
about Deuteronomy 28 and everything

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:31.390
about sickness and disease, Jesus paid

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:33.990
the price for you to walk in victory

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:36.630
over sickness and disease. Find

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:39.429
scriptures to stand on. That's what we do

00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:41.710
in this house for every single thing we

00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:45.190
ever have need

00:01:45.190 --> 00:01:45.200
of—physically,

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.310
financially, spiritually,

00:01:47.310 --> 00:01:47.320
or

00:01:47.320 --> 00:01:50.270
emotionally. Jesus paid the price for you

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:52.389
to walk in victory. I just want to

00:01:52.399 --> 00:01:55.149
encourage you today: find

00:01:55.159 --> 00:01:57.510
scriptures. Google it. If you don't have

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:00.190
Google on your phone, find a Bible app,

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:02.870
put in there 'healing scriptures,'and read

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.950
those scriptures. Meditate on

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.389
that word. Get that word down inside of

00:02:07.399 --> 00:02:09.550
your heart, and the word

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:11.790
will become real to you and

00:02:11.800 --> 00:02:15.470
change your life. Every single day,

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:17.710
get in that word. If the

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:20.110
doctors prescribed you medicine,

00:02:20.120 --> 00:02:22.350
take the

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:24.430
medicine and take the word. Read that

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:27.229
word; let it go in through your eyes and

00:02:27.239 --> 00:02:29.110
get inside your spirit.

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:31.509
The more you feed on that

00:02:31.519 --> 00:02:33.830
word, the more the word becomes real to

00:02:33.840 --> 00:02:36.390
you. Just like when you take a prescription,

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:38.110
sometimes it takes time for it to get in

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:40.110
your system and to help you,

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:42.229
but

00:02:42.229 --> 00:02:42.239
consistency

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:44.990
is the key. I'm

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.110
telling you, get in the word and the word

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:50.350
will change you. Faith calls those things

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:52.309
that be not as though they were. I

00:02:52.319 --> 00:02:54.670
want to encourage you today to call

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:57.270
those things that be not. You may be

00:02:57.280 --> 00:02:59.869
dying or having a bad report;

00:02:59.879 --> 00:03:01.830
call those things that be not as though

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:04.789
they were. 'I am healed by the stripes of

00:03:04.799 --> 00:03:08.430
Jesus. Jesus bore all my sicknesses and

00:03:08.440 --> 00:03:10.830
took all my diseases. I don't have to

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:13.149
have any of that in my body because Jesus

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:15.830
paid the price.'If he took it, I don't

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:17.750
need to bear it.

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:22.350
Satan, I'm not taking your 'poo-poo

00:03:22.350 --> 00:03:22.360
package.'He

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:24.430
comes all the time with the 'poo-poo

00:03:24.430 --> 00:03:24.440
package'full of

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:26.430
all

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:28.710
his doubt, unbelief,

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:30.509
worry, and stuff telling you

00:03:30.519 --> 00:03:32.070
you're going to die, you're not going to

00:03:32.080 --> 00:03:34.750
make it, and there's no hope for you.

00:03:34.760 --> 00:03:37.110
But I'm telling

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:39.630
you, Jesus has a plan for your life and

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:41.789
he has encouragement for you today:

00:03:41.799 --> 00:03:44.550
'Beloved, I wish above all things

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:47.589
that you prosper and be in health, even

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:50.750
as your soul prospers.'Jesus wants you to

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:53.350
be in health and

00:03:53.350 --> 00:03:53.360
prosperity—physically,

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:55.190
spiritually,

00:03:55.190 --> 00:03:55.200
and

00:03:55.200 --> 00:03:57.069
financially. He doesn't want

00:03:57.079 --> 00:04:00.270
anything bad for you. God is a good God

00:04:00.280 --> 00:04:02.429
and the devil is a bad devil. I'm

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:04.710
telling you, he has a plan for your life.

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:04.720
There

00:04:04.720 --> 00:04:07.869
are

00:04:07.879 --> 00:04:10.429
testimonies out there

00:04:12.200 --> 00:04:14.190
about people who have

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:15.870
been

00:04:15.880 --> 00:04:18.870
delivered from sickness and disease.

00:04:18.880 --> 00:04:21.830
I'm standing with a lady for her

00:04:21.840 --> 00:04:23.550
diabetes to be gone, and for Joyce with her

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:26.350
kidneys.

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:28.950
We

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:30.990
are believing for

00:04:30.990 --> 00:04:31.000
the

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:32.749
manifestation of

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:35.550
whatever they need.

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.350
Sometimes there's a process. We see

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:41.230
healing gradually sometimes, but

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:43.029
sometimes it's instantaneous. No

00:04:43.029 --> 00:04:43.039
matter

00:04:43.039 --> 00:04:45.830
how you get your manifestation,

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:48.670
it's like

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:51.469
when

00:04:51.479 --> 00:04:55.790
Noah sent out the dove to go

00:04:55.800 --> 00:04:58.749
find land and he came back with an olive

00:04:58.749 --> 00:04:58.759
leaf—just

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:02.870
a little bitty thing. It

00:05:02.880 --> 00:05:05.830
wasn't a huge

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:08.469
sycamore tree leaf; it was just a little

00:05:08.479 --> 00:05:11.029
bitty thing, but it gave him

00:05:11.039 --> 00:05:13.350
encouragement to know the flood was

00:05:13.360 --> 00:05:15.790
over. There's a change

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:18.390
coming.

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:21.070
You may just get that little

00:05:21.080 --> 00:05:24.270
bitty glimmer of hope.

00:05:24.280 --> 00:05:27.430
Don't say, 'It's too small

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:29.990
a thing.'No, that means

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:32.110
something's changing. We already see the

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:34.510
ship turning around. You've got to get

00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:36.990
excited whenever you see just

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:39.870
a little bitty leaf.

00:05:39.870 --> 00:05:39.880
That

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:42.590
little dove put it in its little

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:44.309
beak—a

00:05:44.319 --> 00:05:47.029
little bitty bird

00:05:47.039 --> 00:05:48.590
went out there and grabbed a hold of

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.350
something and brought it back for

00:05:50.360 --> 00:05:52.110
encouragement, showing

00:05:52.110 --> 00:05:52.120
that

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:54.990
the flood's over. Today

00:05:54.990 --> 00:05:55.000
is

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:57.710
your day of turnaround.

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:02.189
Don't despise

00:06:02.199 --> 00:06:04.790
small beginnings. Get excited about the

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:05.990
little things. That's what I do with my

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:08.749
daughter Megan.

00:06:08.759 --> 00:06:11.469
We went to church as a family and

00:06:11.479 --> 00:06:13.070
sat in one of the most

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:15.510
amazing churches in Tulsa, Oklahoma,

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.029
this last

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:20.909
week. It blessed us a lot. We hadn't been

00:06:20.919 --> 00:06:22.670
to church

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:25.350
in a long time

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.469
because

00:06:26.479 --> 00:06:28.550
ushers have often asked us to leave

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:30.870
because Megan was causing a commotion and

00:06:30.870 --> 00:06:30.880
was

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:33.390
disruptive.

00:06:35.919 --> 00:06:39.029
But this time she didn't act out.

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:40.950
I just want to tell you all, that was a

00:06:40.960 --> 00:06:42.790
miracle in itself. Nobody even knew

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:44.430
it, because nobody knew us at this church,

00:06:44.440 --> 00:06:47.909
but it was a miracle.

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:50.749
Regardless of how small it may have

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:52.870
been in somebody's eyes, it was a big

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:55.309
miracle to us. We saw that

00:06:55.319 --> 00:06:57.830
little leaf in that dove's mouth and

00:06:57.840 --> 00:07:00.150
we rejoiced all the way home

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:02.550
and gave God the praise for it.

00:07:05.599 --> 00:07:07.790
Another testimony

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:12.350
about her: for 14 years, she wouldn't

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:16.029
go to the dentist. They

00:07:16.039 --> 00:07:17.749
weren't able to touch her teeth because

00:07:17.759 --> 00:07:19.869
she'd bite them.

00:07:19.879 --> 00:07:24.070
Then one day, I told

00:07:24.080 --> 00:07:27.510
Megan, 'Hey baby, Daddy's taking you

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:29.710
to the dentist tomorrow.

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:31.830
Please don't bite the doctor; keep your

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:33.869
mouth open.'I got some

00:07:33.879 --> 00:07:36.670
tools from Amazon and I tried to pretend

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:39.230
like I was the dentist,

00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:45.909
practicing. We went to the

00:07:45.919 --> 00:07:49.149
dentist that day, and she got X-rays

00:07:49.149 --> 00:07:49.159
and

00:07:49.159 --> 00:07:51.790
a full cleaning. She let

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.350
the doctor open her mouth and look in

00:07:53.360 --> 00:07:55.430
there, and after all those years, she

00:07:55.440 --> 00:07:57.550
didn't have one cavity. What I'm trying

00:07:57.560 --> 00:07:59.830
to tell you is that you can't give up

00:07:59.830 --> 00:07:59.840
when

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:02.510
it seems impossible and

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:04.350
looks like it's never going to change.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:07.469
You've got to believe God and

00:08:07.479 --> 00:08:10.830
know that all things are possible to him

00:08:10.840 --> 00:08:13.070
who believes. This was one of those

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:16.189
things that seemed impossible.

00:08:21.599 --> 00:08:24.790
But God, who is rich

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:28.670
in Mercy, made it possible. We stood

00:08:28.670 --> 00:08:28.680
for that for

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:34.709
14 years.

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:40.509
Then, for 17 years, we believed for her to be

00:08:40.519 --> 00:08:44.509
potty trained.

00:08:50.360 --> 00:08:54.310
One day she

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:56.190
woke up, went and sat on the

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.190
stool,

00:09:00.720 --> 00:09:02.870
and she's never had an accident since. She's

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:04.829
been potty trained

00:09:04.829 --> 00:09:04.839
ever since.

00:09:04.839 --> 00:09:07.750
God's been faithful.

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:10.030
It took 17

00:09:10.040 --> 00:09:14.910
going on 18 years of no change, and

00:09:14.910 --> 00:09:14.920
then

00:09:14.920 --> 00:09:18.230
suddenly it changed overnight.

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:20.430
What

00:09:20.440 --> 00:09:22.310
seems impossible in your life,

00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:25.030
God can

00:09:25.030 --> 00:09:25.040
turn

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:27.990
around. I want to show you

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:31.430
these testimonies about people God

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:34.030
touched. A boy had

00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:37.230
cancer; another woman had incurable

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:39.710
heart disease.

00:09:39.720 --> 00:09:42.350
Jesus

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:44.870
will touch you, too. He's no respecter

00:09:44.870 --> 00:09:44.880
of persons,

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:46.550
and what

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:49.509
he'll do for one, he will do for you.

00:09:51.839 --> 00:09:54.110
I'll be right back after these

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:56.150
testimonies, and I'm going to come

00:09:56.160 --> 00:09:58.269
and pray for you today. I

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:08.190
worked

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:11.550
at Victory Church for

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:15.389
about 13 years and started

00:10:15.399 --> 00:10:17.590
getting the reputation that if I

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.790
prayed for you, Jesus would heal you.

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:23.230
There was this

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:28.150
lady whose little boy was diagnosed

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:30.470
with cancer that was

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:33.310
eating up the side of his

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:36.590
face. I was

00:10:36.600 --> 00:10:39.629
the janitor there, and I was

00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:42.269
cleaning a room

00:10:42.269 --> 00:10:42.279
when

00:10:42.279 --> 00:10:43.790
she

00:10:43.800 --> 00:10:46.310
came

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:49.230
to me and said, 'Hey

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:53.030
Brandon, I heard that if you would

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:55.829
pray for my little boy,

00:10:57.600 --> 00:11:01.509
God would heal him.'He was

00:11:01.509 --> 00:11:01.519
about seven

00:11:01.519 --> 00:11:05.350
or eight

00:11:05.350 --> 00:11:05.360
years old.

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:07.269
She said

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:10.350
he had a massive tumor on the

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:11.509
side of his

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:14.230
face. It was

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:16.190
shocking because it

00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:18.310
was the size of a mandarin orange.

00:11:23.519 --> 00:11:27.829
I laid hands on that tumor,

00:11:27.839 --> 00:11:31.150
cursed it, and told it to go in

00:11:31.160 --> 00:11:34.430
the name of Jesus. I felt electricity

00:11:34.440 --> 00:11:36.990
go out of my fingers, and the power of

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.509
God went into that tumor.

00:11:38.519 --> 00:11:40.389
I

00:11:40.399 --> 00:11:43.509
told

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:46.710
her

00:11:46.710 --> 00:11:46.720
to

00:11:46.720 --> 00:11:49.550
rejoice for

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:50.870
the rest of the night because I believed

00:11:50.870 --> 00:11:50.880
the Lord was

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:52.670
healing that tumor.

00:12:15.320 --> 00:12:19.069
The next week, she came back and

00:12:19.069 --> 00:12:19.079
said

00:12:19.079 --> 00:12:21.590
she took her

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:25.189
son to the

00:12:25.189 --> 00:12:25.199
doctor

00:12:25.199 --> 00:12:29.269
to get a

00:12:29.269 --> 00:12:29.279
certificate

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:31.389
of health.

00:12:31.399 --> 00:12:34.710
That tumor was completely

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:38.310
gone.

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:50.189
The doctor said he'd never seen

00:12:50.199 --> 00:12:52.069
anything like it and tried to say it had to be a

00:12:52.069 --> 00:12:52.079
plugged lymph node because

00:12:52.079 --> 00:12:54.829
cancer

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:06.870
doesn't

00:13:06.880 --> 00:13:09.750
just disappear. But she told

00:13:09.750 --> 00:13:09.760
him about

00:13:09.760 --> 00:13:11.389
all the blood work and

00:13:11.389 --> 00:13:11.399
the

00:13:11.399 --> 00:13:13.230
chemo

00:13:13.230 --> 00:13:13.240
they

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:15.150
were wanting to start.

00:13:21.839 --> 00:13:23.629
They tried to downplay it,

00:13:23.639 --> 00:13:25.990
but we both knew—I touched

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:28.949
it, and it was really gnarly.

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:32.550
But God touched that little boy.

00:13:34.670 --> 00:13:34.680
Now,

00:13:36.399 --> 00:13:38.790
another testimony.

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:46.550
I was mowing my grandmother's

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:49.710
yard. She's

00:13:49.720 --> 00:13:52.749
almost 90, and I try to

00:13:52.759 --> 00:13:55.749
help her out.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:59.790
I was just minding my own business,

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:01.189
praying

00:14:01.199 --> 00:14:03.389
in the spirit

00:14:03.399 --> 00:14:04.990
while I

00:14:04.990 --> 00:14:05.000
mowed.

00:14:05.000 --> 00:14:08.870
There was this

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:12.389
African-American man walking down

00:14:12.399 --> 00:14:16.590
the street with an oxygen tank.

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:28.430
He was a weird shade of gray,

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:32.670
and

00:14:32.680 --> 00:14:35.629
he

00:14:46.639 --> 00:14:49.949
was gasping for air.

00:14:56.079 --> 00:15:00.030
The Lord said, 'Get

00:15:00.040 --> 00:15:02.269
off that mower right now and go pray

00:15:02.279 --> 00:15:03.189
for that

00:15:09.550 --> 00:15:09.560
man.'I

00:15:13.880 --> 00:15:16.269
wrestled with

00:15:16.279 --> 00:15:20.230
it for a bit,

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:21.910
but

00:15:21.920 --> 00:15:24.749
then

00:15:24.759 --> 00:15:27.509
I

00:15:27.519 --> 00:15:29.030
obeyed.

00:15:29.040 --> 00:15:32.710
I walked down and

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:34.949
told

00:15:37.949 --> 00:15:37.959
him,

00:15:40.120 --> 00:15:43.430
'This may sound wild,

00:15:43.440 --> 00:15:45.949
but

00:15:45.959 --> 00:15:48.189
the Lord told me to

00:15:48.199 --> 00:15:50.269
come pray for

00:15:50.279 --> 00:15:53.910
you. Is it okay?'He looked flustered and said,

00:15:59.800 --> 00:16:02.949
'I guess so. I'm

00:16:02.949 --> 00:16:02.959
dying.'He

00:16:02.959 --> 00:16:06.230
had

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:08.910
sprayed

00:16:08.920 --> 00:16:12.150
Roundup on ditches for the government

00:16:12.160 --> 00:16:15.189
for 35 years, and

00:16:15.189 --> 00:16:15.199
the

00:16:15.199 --> 00:16:20.030
toxic fumes

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:22.949
destroyed his lungs. He

00:16:22.949 --> 00:16:22.959
needed

00:16:22.959 --> 00:16:24.629
a lung transplant and the doctor

00:16:24.639 --> 00:16:26.509
said

00:16:26.519 --> 00:16:29.189
he

00:16:32.990 --> 00:16:33.000
was

00:16:34.839 --> 00:16:37.389
dying.

00:16:39.240 --> 00:16:42.189
I took authority over his lungs

00:16:42.189 --> 00:16:42.199
and

00:16:42.199 --> 00:16:43.949
prayed.

00:16:43.949 --> 00:16:43.959
I

00:16:43.959 --> 00:16:47.110
didn't feel

00:16:47.110 --> 00:16:47.120
anything—it

00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:49.350
was

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:51.150
like

00:16:51.160 --> 00:16:55.749
touching a cold stove.

00:16:55.749 --> 00:16:55.759
But

00:16:58.430 --> 00:16:58.440
I

00:16:58.440 --> 00:17:00.470
told

00:17:00.480 --> 00:17:02.150
him,

00:17:02.160 --> 00:17:04.429
'I believe you're healed

00:17:09.839 --> 00:17:12.029
today.'A

00:17:16.959 --> 00:17:21.309
couple of weeks

00:17:21.309 --> 00:17:21.319
later,

00:17:21.319 --> 00:17:24.990
he

00:17:24.990 --> 00:17:25.000
ran

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:29.909
up to me. He said

00:17:31.799 --> 00:17:35.590
he'd

00:17:40.760 --> 00:17:44.630
been

00:17:44.640 --> 00:17:48.789
completely healed,

00:17:48.789 --> 00:17:48.799
with

00:17:48.799 --> 00:17:51.990
two

00:17:51.990 --> 00:17:52.000
brand-new

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:54.789
lungs.

00:17:56.760 --> 00:17:58.990
They took him off the donor list

00:17:58.990 --> 00:17:59.000
and he didn't

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:00.510
need

00:18:00.510 --> 00:18:00.520
the

00:18:00.520 --> 00:18:02.990
oxygen

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:05.870
tank

00:18:08.559 --> 00:18:11.270
anymore.

00:18:12.960 --> 00:18:15.909
His skin was

00:18:15.909 --> 00:18:15.919
back

00:18:15.919 --> 00:18:19.350
to

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:21.950
its

00:18:21.950 --> 00:18:21.960
healthy

00:18:21.960 --> 00:18:24.990
color.

00:18:25.000 --> 00:18:28.070
He

00:18:28.080 --> 00:18:29.390
wasn't even a Christian yet,

00:18:29.390 --> 00:18:29.400
so

00:18:29.400 --> 00:18:31.029
I

00:18:31.029 --> 00:18:31.039
witnessed

00:18:31.039 --> 00:18:33.669
to him

00:19:04.350 --> 00:19:04.360
and

00:19:42.120 --> 00:19:44.950
led him to the Lord.

00:19:46.549 --> 00:19:46.559
Now,

00:19:52.590 --> 00:19:52.600
another

00:19:55.000 --> 00:19:56.430
story.

00:19:58.320 --> 00:20:01.510
I was leading

00:20:01.520 --> 00:20:04.990
prayer on a Saturday.

00:20:07.080 --> 00:20:10.669
Suddenly,

00:20:12.559 --> 00:20:13.950
I

00:20:17.630 --> 00:20:17.640
saw

00:20:22.070 --> 00:20:22.080
an

00:20:26.880 --> 00:20:30.230
angel

00:20:30.230 --> 00:20:30.240
dive-bomb

00:20:30.240 --> 00:20:32.430
from

00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:34.470
the

00:20:34.480 --> 00:20:37.470
ceiling

00:20:37.480 --> 00:20:39.430
like a

00:20:44.480 --> 00:20:47.590
rocket with a heart in his

00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:51.110
hand. He dropped that heart

00:21:03.600 --> 00:21:05.310
inside a lady's

00:21:05.320 --> 00:21:08.590
chest. I called her up and told her the Lord

00:21:08.590 --> 00:21:08.600
wanted to heal

00:21:08.600 --> 00:21:11.149
her.

00:21:29.760 --> 00:21:31.950
The power of God knocked her down,

00:21:31.960 --> 00:21:33.909
and she was

00:21:33.919 --> 00:21:35.870
crying and

00:21:37.159 --> 00:21:40.190
rejoicing.

00:21:45.799 --> 00:21:50.310
The

00:21:50.320 --> 00:21:51.990
next week,

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:53.950
she ran into the church

00:21:53.960 --> 00:21:56.710
so excited. She

00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:04.029
had a doctor's

00:22:04.039 --> 00:22:07.029
appointment

00:22:07.039 --> 00:22:09.350
and told the doctor she believed

00:22:09.350 --> 00:22:09.360
she was

00:22:09.360 --> 00:22:11.190
healed.

00:22:12.799 --> 00:22:15.590
She had started

00:22:15.600 --> 00:22:18.070
exercising

00:22:20.520 --> 00:22:22.070
and

00:22:23.919 --> 00:22:26.149
jogging

00:22:26.159 --> 00:22:27.590
without

00:22:27.600 --> 00:22:28.830
getting winded.

00:22:28.840 --> 00:22:30.990
The doctor checked

00:22:30.990 --> 00:22:31.000
her

00:22:31.000 --> 00:22:33.750
heart and was shocked—it

00:22:33.750 --> 00:22:33.760
was like brand-new.

00:22:33.760 --> 00:22:36.590
He

00:22:38.470 --> 00:22:38.480
gave

00:22:40.400 --> 00:22:42.149
her

00:23:09.919 --> 00:23:12.510
a certificate of

00:23:12.520 --> 00:23:14.830
health.

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:38.830
She told me

00:23:38.830 --> 00:23:38.840
her

00:23:38.840 --> 00:23:41.909
husband

00:23:41.909 --> 00:23:41.919
was

00:23:41.919 --> 00:23:46.190
a

00:23:46.190 --> 00:23:46.200
Jewish

00:23:46.200 --> 00:23:48.669
atheist

00:23:48.669 --> 00:23:48.679
who

00:23:48.679 --> 00:23:51.750
was

00:23:51.760 --> 00:23:54.750
angry because

00:23:54.760 --> 00:23:56.990
her

00:23:57.000 --> 00:23:58.909
heart

00:23:58.919 --> 00:24:01.990
condition prevented her from

00:24:01.990 --> 00:24:02.000
doing anything at

00:24:02.000 --> 00:24:04.870
home. But because

00:24:04.870 --> 00:24:04.880
of her healing,

00:24:04.880 --> 00:24:07.789
he gave

00:24:07.799 --> 00:24:10.470
his heart to

00:24:10.480 --> 00:24:12.310
Jesus

00:24:12.320 --> 00:24:14.149
and

00:24:14.159 --> 00:24:16.149
started coming to

00:24:16.159 --> 00:24:18.070
church.

00:24:29.679 --> 00:24:34.190
The doctor

00:24:38.909 --> 00:24:38.919
had

00:24:42.679 --> 00:24:44.750
said if they even tried surgery

00:24:44.750 --> 00:24:44.760
on her artery, she wouldn't

00:24:44.760 --> 00:24:46.630
make it.

00:24:46.640 --> 00:24:49.510
But

00:24:52.070 --> 00:24:52.080
God

00:24:55.640 --> 00:24:57.789
completely healed

00:25:04.159 --> 00:25:06.750
her.

00:25:12.159 --> 00:25:15.430
Jesus Christ is the same yesterday,

00:25:15.440 --> 00:25:18.070
today, and forever.

00:25:22.360 --> 00:25:24.630
Look at

00:25:24.640 --> 00:25:26.950
the

00:25:26.960 --> 00:25:29.029
story of the woman with the issue of

00:25:29.039 --> 00:25:33.149
blood. She spent all she had

00:25:38.240 --> 00:25:39.830
and

00:25:41.799 --> 00:25:45.909
grew worse, but she touched the

00:25:45.919 --> 00:25:49.190
hem of his garment and

00:25:53.000 --> 00:25:56.350
virtue went out of him. Virtue is

00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:58.470
going to come through this

00:25:58.480 --> 00:26:01.389
camera

00:26:01.399 --> 00:26:05.710
today.

00:26:10.440 --> 00:26:12.710
Just like

00:26:14.600 --> 00:26:17.950
with blind Bartimaeus, son of

00:26:17.950 --> 00:26:17.960
Timaeus,

00:26:17.960 --> 00:26:20.350
if he

00:26:20.360 --> 00:26:22.630
did it then, he'll do it now. You just

00:26:22.630 --> 00:26:22.640
have

00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:24.789
to have simple faith.

00:26:35.480 --> 00:26:39.029
Go watch my video about the

00:26:39.039 --> 00:26:41.110
crucifixion.

00:26:51.600 --> 00:26:54.269
Jesus took me out

00:26:54.269 --> 00:26:54.279
of my

00:26:54.279 --> 00:26:56.470
body and

00:26:56.470 --> 00:26:56.480
showed me

00:26:56.480 --> 00:26:59.549
what he did for us on that cross.

00:26:59.559 --> 00:27:02.549
Let's pray for your miracle today. I'm

00:27:02.559 --> 00:27:06.070
going to agree with you.

00:27:06.080 --> 00:27:08.470
Where

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:10.950
two are touching and agreeing, let's

00:27:10.960 --> 00:27:13.230
do it

00:27:14.440 --> 00:27:16.430
by faith through the camera.

00:27:21.159 --> 00:27:22.830
You may have

00:27:22.840 --> 00:27:25.070
AIDS, cancer,

00:27:25.070 --> 00:27:25.080
or

00:27:27.389 --> 00:27:27.399
diabetes—nothing

00:27:28.990 --> 00:27:29.000
is

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:32.190
too

00:27:32.200 --> 00:27:35.549
big.

00:27:35.559 --> 00:27:38.990
Father, I thank you

00:27:39.000 --> 00:27:42.350
right now for every single

00:27:42.350 --> 00:27:42.360
person

00:27:42.360 --> 00:27:44.669
believing for a

00:27:44.679 --> 00:27:47.789
manifestation of healing.

00:28:14.159 --> 00:28:17.190
We call them healed, whole,

00:28:17.200 --> 00:28:21.549
and well

00:28:26.760 --> 00:28:28.230
in

00:28:33.320 --> 00:28:35.710
Jesus'name.

00:28:40.360 --> 00:28:42.950
We call healing over

00:28:42.960 --> 00:28:46.269
stroke victims,

00:28:51.600 --> 00:28:54.470
arthritis,

00:28:54.470 --> 00:28:54.480
diabetes,

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:57.430
and

00:28:57.430 --> 00:28:57.440
heart

00:28:57.440 --> 00:29:00.269
disease.

00:29:00.279 --> 00:29:02.190
We're calling those things that

00:29:02.200 --> 00:29:04.750
be not as though they were.

00:29:11.600 --> 00:29:14.470
We call the

00:29:14.480 --> 00:29:18.190
manifestation done

00:29:21.600 --> 00:29:24.950
now. Faith is

00:29:24.950 --> 00:29:24.960
the

00:29:24.960 --> 00:29:27.669
substance of things hoped for and

00:29:27.669 --> 00:29:27.679
the

00:29:27.679 --> 00:29:31.190
evidence of things not seen.

00:29:31.200 --> 00:29:35.590
We receive your

00:29:35.600 --> 00:29:38.909
healing power

00:29:38.919 --> 00:29:43.710
from all disease

00:29:43.710 --> 00:29:43.720
and

00:29:43.720 --> 00:29:47.029
demonic oppression.

00:29:56.080 --> 00:29:59.630
PTSD, I command you to leave right

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:04.990
now in the name of Jesus.

00:30:08.480 --> 00:30:11.590
I call you delivered from the

00:30:30.440 --> 00:30:31.870
flashbacks and

00:30:31.880 --> 00:30:33.789
for

00:30:33.799 --> 00:30:36.830
your mind to

00:30:36.840 --> 00:30:39.909
be lined up with the word of God.

00:30:39.919 --> 00:30:42.070
Second Timothy

00:30:42.080 --> 00:30:45.669
1:7 says God has not given you a spirit of fear

00:30:45.679 --> 00:30:48.149
but of power, love, and a

00:30:48.149 --> 00:30:48.159
sound

00:30:48.159 --> 00:30:51.350
mind.

00:30:53.880 --> 00:30:56.830
Father, I thank you

00:30:56.830 --> 00:30:56.840
for

00:30:56.840 --> 00:30:58.870
the

00:30:58.880 --> 00:31:01.710
children with autism,

00:31:01.720 --> 00:31:03.789
Down

00:31:05.870 --> 00:31:05.880
syndrome,

00:31:08.240 --> 00:31:11.029
cerebral

00:31:14.509 --> 00:31:14.519
palsy,

00:31:17.080 --> 00:31:20.549
or

00:31:20.559 --> 00:31:22.909
learning disabilities. We call

00:31:22.919 --> 00:31:25.430
healing and wholeness over

00:31:25.440 --> 00:31:28.590
their bodies in the name of Jesus. We

00:31:28.600 --> 00:31:30.710
thank you that

00:31:30.710 --> 00:31:30.720
you bore

00:31:30.720 --> 00:31:33.110
it all on the cross. We thank

00:31:33.120 --> 00:31:35.350
you

00:31:51.080 --> 00:31:53.909
for deliverance from drugs and alcohol.

00:31:53.919 --> 00:31:55.509
I

00:31:55.519 --> 00:31:59.389
call

00:31:59.399 --> 00:32:02.830
cirrhosis

00:32:02.840 --> 00:32:05.669
of the liver healed and whole.

00:32:14.600 --> 00:32:16.950
Drug

00:32:16.960 --> 00:32:19.389
addictions,

00:32:19.399 --> 00:32:22.629
meth,

00:32:26.509 --> 00:32:26.519
opioids—we

00:32:33.760 --> 00:32:36.590
call them delivered.

00:32:38.200 --> 00:32:41.509
We thank you

00:32:41.519 --> 00:32:44.430
for marriages being restored and families coming back together. We call

00:33:14.269 --> 00:33:14.279
the

00:33:48.559 --> 00:33:50.190
generational

00:33:50.200 --> 00:33:52.990
curses and strongholds

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:55.590
broken in

00:33:55.590 --> 00:33:55.600
Jesus'name.

00:33:55.600 --> 00:33:57.909
You

00:33:57.909 --> 00:33:57.919
are

00:33:57.919 --> 00:33:59.590
set free from

00:34:12.760 --> 00:34:15.629
alcoholism

00:34:19.839 --> 00:34:22.510
and

00:34:27.430 --> 00:34:27.440
addiction.

00:34:35.320 --> 00:34:38.230
You walk in victory. Jesus

00:34:47.760 --> 00:34:51.270
loves you

00:34:51.280 --> 00:34:53.470
and

00:34:55.069 --> 00:34:55.079
doesn't

00:34:57.880 --> 00:34:59.950
want you to suffer.

00:34:59.960 --> 00:35:03.589
He wants you to

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:11.190
have a good life and

00:35:11.190 --> 00:35:11.200
an

00:35:11.200 --> 00:35:13.710
expected end.

00:35:13.720 --> 00:35:16.150
I hope this

00:35:16.160 --> 00:35:19.829
encouraged you. If

00:35:19.839 --> 00:35:22.870
it did, please

00:35:22.880 --> 00:35:25.430
subscribe,

00:35:25.440 --> 00:35:27.829
click the notification

00:35:27.839 --> 00:35:30.069
bell, and give a thumbs up.

00:35:30.079 --> 00:35:32.310
Comment down below

00:35:32.320 --> 00:35:34.990
if you were healed

00:35:34.990 --> 00:35:35.000
or

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:37.270
set free

00:35:39.760 --> 00:35:41.589
today.

00:35:43.680 --> 00:35:46.630
People need to hear

00:35:46.640 --> 00:35:50.589
encouragement.

00:36:03.760 --> 00:36:05.910
God bless you

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:08.550
all in

00:36:08.550 --> 00:36:08.560
Jesus'name.

00:36:08.560 --> 00:36:10.910
Put a smile on your face and

00:36:10.920 --> 00:36:13.750
a song in your heart.

00:36:13.750 --> 00:36:13.760
We'll

00:36:13.760 --> 00:36:16.349
see you

00:36:16.359 --> 00:36:18.790
next time.

00:36:18.800 --> 00:36:22.240
Bye-bye.

